title: Need a duo partner to play with me to gold
body: Im Silver 2 and i main Sup Brand, im really good with him and i need a good adc or anyone that can duo with me and help me reach Gold.

replies.body: Hey man, I'm a Silver 4 ADC main, l'm mastery 7 on Jinx, Jhin, Ashe, and Vayne (I'm a Vayne main, Over 460k mastery on her) i also play all other ADCs well and very experienced with them as l'm mastery 5 with almost all ADCs
Sup brand... Sounds a bit dodgy but I play Jhin adc. Look at my match history with him and I'll let you decide on it.
